===Noun===
'''plod'''
#A [[slow]] or [[labored]] [[walk]] or other [[motion]] or [[activity]].
#:''We started at a brisk walk and ended at a '''plod'''.''

===Verb===
'''plod'''
#(intransitive) To [[walk]] or [[move]] [[slowly]] and [[heavily]] or [[laboriously]].
#:''They '''plodded''' through the mud, discouraged and tired.''

